OL,3,CMan in court charged with manslaughter
OL,4,Cof Sam Rees
OL,6,FA man has appeared in court accused of
OL,7,Fmanslaughter, after another man died
OL,8,Fin 2023, 10 years after being
OL,9,Fassaulted.
OL,11,FSam Rees, 27, was attacked in 2013 and
OL,12,Fleft with a significant head injury in
OL,13,Fthe Old Town area of the town.
OL,15,FAt the time, Abuzer Erdem, 40, of
OL,16,FFerndale Road, Swindon, was jailed for
OL,17,F12 months for inflicting grievous
OL,18,Fbodily harm.
OL,20,FMr Rees required full-time care until
OL,21,Fhis death on 22 December 2023.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/4
