CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F438A1779894668
OL,3,CMan in court charged with manslaughter
OL,4,Cof Sam Rees
OL,6,FFollowing his death, Erdem was then
OL,7,Fcharged with manslaughter after
OL,8,FWiltshire Police reopened the
OL,9,Finvestigation into the original attack
OL,10,Fagainst Rees.
OL,12,FOn the morning of Tuesday 26 May, he
OL,13,Fappeared at Swindon Magistrates Court.
OL,15,FHe spoke only to confirm his personal
OL,16,Fdetails, made no plea and was released
OL,17,Fon bail until his next appearance
OL,18,Fscheduled for Swindon Crown Court on
OL,19,F10 July.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/4
