OL,3,CMan in court charged with manslaughter
OL,4,Cof Sam Rees
OL,6,FFollowing the reopening of the
OL,7,Finvestigation, Detective Constable
OL,8,FJemma Humphreys, of the Major Crime
OL,9,FInvestigation Team of Wiltshire Police
OL,10,Fsaid:
OL,12,F"This is a tragic case of a young man
OL,13,Fwho suffered significant injuries
OL,14,Ffollowing an assault in Swindon and
OL,15,Ftragically died 10 years later."
